data.description: NEW LISTING! This open-concept floor plan home is located in the quaint community of Kittery Subdivision in Snellville.  The home features beautiful hardwood floors throughout the main level, kitchen w/breakfast area overlooking a spacious great room.  Large Dining Room for dinner parties.  Beautiful matching chandeliers located in dining room, great room, living room and foyer! The upstairs has an oversized master bedroom with sitting area, and a large walk-in closet.  The master bath also has a closet, double vanities, separate shower & soaking tub. Right next to the master is a bedroom great for an office, theatre room, nursery or 5th bedroom.  There are also two secondary bedrooms on the opposite side from the master just on the other side of the beautiful catwalk. Great backyard for entertaining; Close to Stone Mountain Park; Lots of dining and shopping; just minutes from Snellville's The Town Green
